title: Ep. 763 - The Banter Continues - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The puja has started in the society of Gokuldham. Jetha and others are a witness to it. But, the brother - in - laws banter doesn't seem to end.

title: Ep. 764 - The Morning Routine - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya is scared as she sees a cockroach. Champaklal goes for his daily morning walk. While coming back he encounters a person spitting on the road and teaches him a lesson.

title: Ep. 765 - A Revenge - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Vicky drops Champaklal home but he has an ugly motive. Meanwhile, Iyer comes to Jetha's house for help. Meanwhile, Chachaji comes back home with savories for Jetha.

title: Ep. 766 - Posters OF Chacha Ji - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Vicky sticks all the posters of Chachaji in the town. People are taken aback when Chachaji goes through there. What will be the consequences?

title: Ep. 767 - The Trouble Game - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Chachaji is duped by two strangers and is taken to his house. The residents form a human chain and help Chachaji from his troubles.

title: Ep. 768 - Will Tapu Sena Help? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Chachaji understands the reason behind these problems. He explains the same to Tapu and the others. Tapu Sena hurries and goes to find the culprit.

title: Ep. 769 - A Solution - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha and the others run behind Tapu Sena to stop them. Meanwhile, after being tired, Jetha goes to his shop and explains the story to Nattu kaka and Baga. They come up with a solution.

title: Ep. 770 - Will The Culprit Be Found? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: With Natu Kaka and Baga's poster, many people make queues in front of Gada electronics to claim the cash prize. But, will the real culprit be caught?

title: Ep. 771 - Relentless Attempts - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: While Sodhi and Popatlal are out to find Vicky, he comes up with a plan of trapping Chachaji yet again. He distributes more posters with more cash prize. Champaklal is furious and wants to find him.

title: Ep. 772 - Where Is Chacha Ji? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Chachaji runs for his life. Meanwhile, Jetha gets a call that Chachaji is missing. Sodhi, Bhide, and others are out to find him. Chachaji gets into a car's boot. How will he come out?

title: Ep. 773 - A Realization - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Vicky is out with his friend and realizes the mistake he has done. He indeed wants to help him out. Chachaji finally comes out of the boot. But, the search is still on for him.

title: Ep. 774 - Chachaji Comes Home - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Chachaji's identity is mistaken. He was to be taken to a mental asylum. Meanwhile, the search still continues. Later, everybody is happy to see Chachaji at home.

title: Ep. 775 - Vicky Apologizes - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Chachaji doesn't scold Vicky but he finally apologizes to him. Later, Jethalal decided that on this occasion a party should be organized.

title: Ep. 776 - A Happy Day - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak and Anjali mock each other about their group of friends. Jetha is still confused about whether to give the part to not as he gets many advices. What will he finally do?

title: Ep. 777 - Jetha's Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha comes up with a plan to surprise the people of Gokuldham. He asks Daya also not to reveal anything. The residents have received the newspapers and the attached pamphlets. will Jetha's plan work out?
